  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this clinical research study is to learn if irbesartan is superior to
      hydrochlorothiazide relative to effects on insulin sensitivity and glucose metabolism in
      hypertensive patients with metabolic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
